{
  "stem": "10446.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And people in Riga were put into a concentration camp outside the city and were shot on short order.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They, they didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another couple was killed right where they lived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was not immediate family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was cousin-- parents of cousins, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of course, which was bad enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was absolutely incredible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was incredible that something like that happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was incredible to, to us that it was permitted to happen without interference.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We felt very strongly that something could have been done, that the concentration camp railroads could have bombed, that some help could have been rendered that was not.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really-- our feelings about Roosevelt, whom we had considered our savior until that time, were completely reversed [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and about Churchill and the other leaders, too.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It really became a feeling of rage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went back to-- Hella and I went back to Germany-- I forgot the exact year-- for one reason only.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wanted to look at the cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went to Nuremberg, and I had the weirdest feeling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Number one, the city has changed from when we lived there because it was bombed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really completely destroyed and very well rebuilt, with some exceptions where suddenly a ultra-modern building stands between some very old, beautifully restored buildings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that is immaterial.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a feeling of not belonging in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't want to see anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had no desire to see any of my former classmates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we did not call anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We stayed at a hotel for, for one night and went to the two cemeteries in, in Nuremberg and got out again and did the same thing several years later.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There we went to-- first to several country cemeteries where our family had been buried in former years, going back to 1700.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And sadly, some of tombstones cannot be located anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The inscription has been completely washed away and weathered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'm still trying to identify some of them, get somebody to do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we stayed-- again, we stayed for one night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, well one thing I must say, that one night was quite interesting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did Hella tell you about that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- the city of Nuremberg, like so many other German cities, invites its former Jewish citizens for a stay of 10 days to two weeks, whatever it may be.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most cities pay for the entire trip.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The city of Nuremberg just pays for the stay there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The, the transportation is your own responsibility.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You pay for the trip.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then they house you, feed you, even give you pocket money for 10 days and take you all over town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You get a reception by the mayor of Nuremberg, and they show you all the sights and are extremely friendly and try-- there's one woman in charge of these affairs.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she is a fabulous person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it so happened that our scheduled visit for the cemetery was-- coincided with the visit of the invitees.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we knew the program.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hella would.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not sure when it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one night, the, the group was invited for the opera in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it so happened that the opera given that night was one that I love and that is never performed in this country.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I wrote to that woman in charge over there and asked if I-- if we could attend.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would certainly pay for our tickets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she wrote back, you have two tickets free of charge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You're free to attend all the affairs for the 10 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only the hotel rooms are fully booked, and the money allocated for that is completely spoken for.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, so we wrote back that we have no way and no intention of staying more than for one night, and we would be very grateful if we could attend the, the opera, which we did.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that-- so we were there with the whole group that was invited for that, for those 10 days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was quite pleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was the best memory of Nuremberg after the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We went to where the temple had been.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there's now a big plaque with an inscription.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at-- on this spot stood the temple, destroyed by the National Socialists in 1938.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we visited the cemeteries, which are in good condition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The cemeteries in Germany are maintained by the state, by the individual states, in our case, the state of Bavaria in Munich.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They don't take care of the individual graves, but of the cemetery in, in general.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
